<ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>P2716</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>Open or short is detected in shift solenoid valve SLT circuit for 1 second or more while driving (1-trip detecting logic).</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
