</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM0000015W100RX_02" type-id="64" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___000061700000">
<name>MONITOR DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>When an open or short in the linear solenoid valve (SLT) circuit is detected, the ECM interprets this as a fault. The ECM will turn on the MIL and store the DTC.</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
